":"dfb3d02260de1e0e880f71c529d4bfea1a686f7c","tid":340710,"uid":124316,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係俾到開心 但唔可靠囉</blockquote><br />\n可靠從信任？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要係講得出做得到<br />\n唔亂應承嘢<br />\n<br />\n有啲事真係需要你嘅時候你係度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做到呢啲--&gt;我可以信任你--&gt;你可靠<br />\n<br />\n利申 自己角度出發<br />\n男朋友唔係好做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b757fc8f79b03008b402adc43e8eff350e95183","tid":340710,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"有能力養你就得啦<br />\n<br />\n比到幸福就叫做老公<br />\n<br />\n只係比得到快樂  就只係男朋友"},{"pid":"f4ebb0f2c7da6702030f757914b06138b2cdfaa6","tid":340710,"uid":69557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"俗語有云, 男人不壞, 女人不愛。<br />\n壞男人可以是個好情人, 但很高機會不是個好老公了。<br />\n(小弟愚見)"},{"pid":"6224cf3b3af64096090d69e8f59dde976540b61d","tid":340710,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"男朋友單純開心就夠，老公要有溫暖嘅感覺，有家嘅感覺"},{"pid":"6a96f43faa7e94200d4a64c7d1fe7570c1140d48","tid":340710,"uid":55937,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:49:49.000Z","msg":"初頭就會話一齊就開心就夠，然後隨著歲月嘅洗禮，要求條件就會增加，做唔到就自然成為唔到&quot;老公&quot;<br />\n<br />\n男仔通常都係貫徹一齊開心就夠嘅諗法，然後就沒有然後了&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f993ca46bd485772a143358c83976b7b8863dd4","tid":340710,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初頭就會話一齊就開心就夠，然後隨著歲月嘅洗禮，要求條件就會增加，做唔到就自然成為唔到&quot;老公&quot;<br />\n<br />\n男仔通常都係貫徹一齊開心就夠嘅諗法，然後就沒有然後了&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25167ab0826803563f3bf72bc860864c8d7a55b0","tid":340710,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:57:17.000Z","msg":"俾人話過性格做老公就好<br />\n做男朋友就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af03cb09d391962bfd5e7624329952de199e598d","tid":340710,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初頭就會話一齊就開心就夠，然後隨著歲月嘅洗禮，要求條件就會增加，做唔到就自然成為唔到&quot;老公&quot;<br />\n<br />\n男仔通常都係貫徹一齊開心就夠嘅諗法，然後就沒有然後了&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要比人話唔長大唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜其實貫徹始終有錯咩&hellip;&hellip;? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始又話要搵純愛，如果之後又係會比雜質影響嘅話，咁一開始就唔應該搵純愛啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac7e5f72b03db4744afd7d96ebd90e91acb0407","tid":340710,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初頭就會話一齊就開心就夠，然後隨著歲月嘅洗禮，要求條件就會增加，做唔到就自然成為唔到&quot;老公&quot;<br />\n<br />\n男仔通常都係貫徹一齊開心就夠嘅諗法，然後就沒有然後了&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSad but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要比人話唔長大唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜其實貫徹始終有錯咩&hellip;&hellip;? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始又話要搵純愛，如果之後又係會比雜質影響嘅話，咁一開始就唔應該搵純愛啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc